{"tid":1291034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新聞百科：港人有出境自由　並無非法出境罪","createTime":"2019-07-06T16:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T17:46:08.000Z","uid":33307,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c37d7e7b8c0b99077ef0690d22e7a5f99ccdc805","tid":1291034,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:57:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20160324/mobile/bkn-20160324195556152-0324_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20160324%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20160324195556152-0324_00822_001.html&d=o%2Fu7L%2BZntrZWbswpyROzR25ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=7671c760\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20160324/mobile/bkn-20160324195556152-0324_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n專門出售內地政治禁書的銅鑼灣書店，其股東李波今午於落馬洲管制站，由入境處人員從深圳出入境機關方面接回香港，李波先後與入境處及警方會面，更要求銷案。港府較早時發新聞稿證實事件，並指由於李波未有提供離境的全面資料，現階段未將其拘捕，入境處需進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">消息指出，《基本法》保障港人有出入境自由，現行法例之下對香港居民亦沒有所謂的「非法出境」及「非法入境」罪行。</span><br />\n<br />\n不過，香港居民無經正常途徑離開香港，不代表沒有干犯任何香港的其他法例，舉例無禁區紙進入禁區範圍，可能違反禁區條例；而若是乘船離港，船主有責任申報船員及乘客，若無申報，亦可能違反香港法例。<br />\n<br />\n據知，鑑於李波無交代他離境時的全面資料，因此現階段並沒有具體證據，證明他有違反香港的任何相關法例，不過入境處仍會繼續調查。另據知，李波今日是以身份證作為入境香港的證明文件。<br />\n<br />\n至於何以較早時回港的銅鑼灣書店職員呂波等人是自行回港，而李波則是被深圳出入境機關「移交」港方？消息人士指，呂波等人是以正常方式進入內地，相信亦因而不需經過內地機關的「移交」過程，可自行離開內地。"},{"pid":"7b5ae35b6e322c91e121722f6defccf5a189d181","tid":1291034,"uid":50457,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:59:04.000Z","msg":"當日李波單野，入境處已經咁講<br />\n<br />\n無一樣野叫非法出境"},{"pid":"45f76dbcf138d7931e326f61de1ddb86c6c6f32d","tid":1291034,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:59:06.000Z","msg":"生活小知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af68bf08224e6bc2eda58be14f8bb52ec31a3e93","tid":1291034,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:01:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7twnFnB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7twnFnB.jpg&h=df2571ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T3Kkr2C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT3Kkr2C.jpg&h=b6c70bc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mTXidHD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmTXidHD.jpg&h=a6d55b00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58b0598c0694b1adf0aee454f4f94f9807315e65","tid":1291034,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b5ae35b6e322c91e121722f6defccf5a189d181","tid":1291034,"uid":50457,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:59:04.000Z","msg":"當日李波單野，入境處已經咁講<br />\n<br />\n無一樣野叫非法出境"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:02:20.000Z","msg":"即係e道其實係廢？"},{"pid":"d1f1ed526e1edb534885cab1e8cdddd16e0318f8","tid":1291034,"uid":62749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:05:13.000Z","msg":"坐船去台灣要幾耐?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b1b9f6e8cb5f1e22e5d90ec22906e4e48bc0e5a","tid":1291034,"uid":174752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:06:23.000Z","msg":"即係我直接衝過香港出境關口冇問題？"},{"pid":"1c12a4e5e1f78f378d6b092fe01030908a0e4eae","tid":1291034,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1f1ed526e1edb534885cab1e8cdddd16e0318f8","tid":1291034,"uid":62749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:05:13.000Z","msg":"坐船去台灣要幾耐?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:19:14.000Z","msg":"澳門高速船黎計要13個鐘<br />\n<br />\n船時速 60 km/h"},{"pid":"c1e9d828be266e89c38c9b9595ec7585b05add4a","tid":1291034,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b1b9f6e8cb5f1e22e5d90ec22906e4e48bc0e5a","tid":1291034,"uid":174752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T17:06